      "content": "thanks. that helps. one more thing—i want to make sure the essay doesn't sound like it's just \"one side\" of a debate. i want to make sure i'm being objective. if i say that wealth redistribution is the only way to achieve racial justice, would that be considered an objective fact in sociology, or am I just presenting a specific ideological viewpoint? like, is there any actual academic consensus on this, or is it just a political debate?",
